{
  "page": "Qartheen gown",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Daenerys_by_carrie_best.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/cb/Daenerys_by_carrie_best.jpg/300px-Daenerys_by_carrie_best.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"375\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/cb/Daenerys_by_carrie_best.jpg/450px-Daenerys_by_carrie_best.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/cb/Daenerys_by_carrie_best.jpg/600px-Daenerys_by_carrie_best.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Daenerys_by_carrie_best.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Daenerys in a <a href=\"/index.php/Qartheen\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Qartheen\">Qartheen</a> gown - by Carrie Best©</div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Mustamirri_Dany_Qartheen_gown.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/37/Mustamirri_Dany_Qartheen_gown.jpg/300px-Mustamirri_Dany_Qartheen_gown.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"503\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/3/37/Mustamirri_Dany_Qartheen_gown.jpg 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Mustamirri_Dany_Qartheen_gown.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Short-haired Daenerys in a <a href=\"/index.php/Qartheen\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Qartheen\">Qartheen</a> gown - by Mustamirri ©</div></div></div>\n<p>A <b>Qartheen gown</b> is a dress worn by <a href=\"/index.php/Qarth\" title=\"Qarth\">Qartheen</a> women. The dress leaves one breast bare. <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> adopted the style during her stay in Qarth and still wears this manner of gown on occasion.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Qartheen_gown&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Qartheen_gown&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>When Daenerys Targaryen first enters the city of Qarth she notices that the Qartheen women are wearing gowns that leave one breast bare.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Later for the audience with the <a href=\"/index.php/Pureborn\" title=\"Pureborn\">Pureborn</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Hall_of_a_Thousand_Thrones\" title=\"Hall of a Thousand Thrones\">Hall of a Thousand Thrones</a> Daenerys has to garb herself in <a href=\"/index.php/Qarth\" title=\"Qarth\">Qartheen</a> fashion, as <a href=\"/index.php/Xaro_Xhoan_Daxos\" title=\"Xaro Xhoan Daxos\">Xaro Xhoan Daxos</a> warns her that the Enthroned will never listen to a <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a>, so she takes care to go before them in flowing green samite <a href=\"/index.php/Qarth\" title=\"Qarth\">Qartheen</a> gown.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>While in the <a href=\"/index.php/House_of_the_Undying\" title=\"House of the Undying\">House of the Undying</a> Daenerys sees a false vision of the <a href=\"/index.php/Undying_Ones\" title=\"Undying Ones\">Undying Ones</a> - a great hall and a splendor of <a href=\"/index.php/Wizard\" title=\"Wizard\">wizards</a>. When a kingly man in rich robes tells Dany (falsely) that they are the Undying of Qarth there is a woman beside him who then tells Dany that they have long awaited her. Dany notices that the woman clad in rose and <a href=\"/index.php/Silver\" title=\"Silver\">silver</a> and that the breast she has left bare in the Qartheen fashion is as perfect as a breast could be. Shortly thereafter, after discovering the real <a href=\"/index.php/Undying_Ones\" title=\"Undying Ones\">Undying Ones</a>, Dany sees that one of them, an ancient woman seated on the opposite side of the table, is wearing a gown of pale <a href=\"/index.php/Silk\" title=\"Silk\">silk</a> that as rotted on her body, one withered breast is left bare in the Qartheen manner.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>When Dany decides that she and her people must flee Qarth she goes down to the <a href=\"/index.php/Port_of_Qarth\" title=\"Port of Qarth\">docks</a> to seek ships passage dressed in <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a> fashion. That morning <a href=\"/index.php/Irri\" title=\"Irri\">Irri</a> had brought her a Qartheen gown to wear, an airy confection of ivory <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/samite\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:samite\">samite</a> patterned with seed pearls, but Dany refused it, telling Irri that the docks are no place for a lady's finery.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok63.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok63.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Qartheen_gown&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>In <a href=\"/index.php/Astapor\" title=\"Astapor\">Astapor</a>, so as not to seem a beggar, Daenerys wears a Qartheen gown and her <a href=\"/index.php/Crown\" title=\"Crown\">crown</a> when she goes to make an offer to the <a href=\"/index.php/Good_Masters\" title=\"Good Masters\">Good Masters</a> of Astapor for all 8,600 <a href=\"/index.php/Unsullied\" title=\"Unsullied\">Unsullied</a>, plus all the <a href=\"/index.php/Slave\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Slave\">slave</a> boys in training. The gown is a deep violet silk, which brings out the <a href=\"/index.php/Purple_eyes\" title=\"Purple eyes\">purple of her eyes</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Qartheen_gown&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>During <a href=\"/index.php/Xaro_Xhoan_Daxos\" title=\"Xaro Xhoan Daxos\">Xaro Xhoan Daxos</a>'s visit to <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a> Dany dons a <a href=\"/index.php/Qarth\" title=\"Qarth\">Qartheen</a> gown in his honour.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Qartheen_gown&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_27\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 27\">Chapter 27</a>, Daenerys II.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_40\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 40\">Chapter 40</a>, Daenerys III.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_48\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 48\">Chapter 48</a>, Daenerys IV.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok63.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok63.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_63\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 63\">Chapter 63</a>, Daenerys V.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos27.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_27\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 27\">Chapter 27</a>, Daenerys III.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd16.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_16\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 16\">Chapter 16</a>, Daenerys III.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:Clothing\" title=\"Template:Clothing\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php?title=Template_talk:Clothing&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Template talk:Clothing (page does not exist)\"><span title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">d</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://awoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?title=Template:Clothing&amp;action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">e</span></a></li></ul></div><div class=\"\" style=\"font-size:110%;\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/Category:Clothing\" title=\"Category:Clothing\">Clothing</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Known_world\" title=\"Known world\">known world</a></div></th></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Fabrics and fibers</td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cot